														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4624983">
									

<p>I always love creative uses for body horror as metaphors for something else, in this case capitalism and worker dehumanization! The visceral snaps, slops, and fizzes the prose places in the reader's mind are an intense, almost sensory experience, and the tale pulls together as an amazing work of dark cyberpunk satire. Easy +1 before And after editing.</p>

